    "subtype": "weapon",
    "text": "As dwarves poured out of the Darklands following their Quest for Sky, the orcs driven before them adapted to their tactics\u2014including dwarves\u2019 heavily armored infantry charges. Surviving orcs developed a response: a weapon that combines a spear and maul to crush heavy armor and skewer charging foes. Although rarely seen today, the weapon is remarkably effective in the right situation.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 159,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
